        "ruleId": "a11y/mouse-events-have-key-events",
        "severity": 1,
        "message": "[vize:a11y/mouse-events-have-key-events] @mouseenter/@mouseover must be paired with @focus for keyboard accessibility",
        "line": 25,
        "column": 7,
        "endLine": 25,
        "endColumn": 80,
        "help": "Why: Keyboard and touch users cannot trigger mouse events.\nFix:\n  <div\n  @mouseenter=\"show\"\n  @mouseleave=\"hide\"\n  @focus=\"show\"\n  @blur=\"hide\"\n  tabindex=\"0\"\n  >\n  Hover or focus me\n  </div>"
      },
      {
        "ruleId": "a11y/click-events-have-key-events",
        "severity": 1,
        "message": "[vize:a11y/click-events-have-key-events] Non-interactive elements with @click must also have keyboard event handlers",
        "line": 28,
        "column": 7,
        "endLine": 28,
        "endColumn": 81,
        "help": "Why: Keyboard users cannot activate click-only handlers.\nBest solution: Use semantic elements:\n  <button @click=\"handleClick\">Click me</button>\nIf you must use a div:\n  <div\n  role=\"button\"\n  tabindex=\"0\"\n  @click=\"handleClick\"\n  @keydown.enter=\"handleClick\"\n  @keydown.space=\"handleClick\"\n  >\n  Click me\n  </div>"
      },
      {
        "ruleId": "a11y/no-static-element-interactions",
        "severity": 1,
        "message": "[vize:a11y/no-static-element-interactions] <a-button> is a static element and should not have interactive event handlers",
        "line": 28,
        "column": 7,
        "endLine": 28,
        "endColumn": 81,
        "help": "Why: Non-interactive elements (div, span, etc.) should not have click/keyboard handlers without a role.\nFix options:\n1. Use a native interactive element:\n  <button @click=\"handle\">Click me</button>\n2. Add role and tabindex:\n  <div role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\" @click=\"handle\">\n  Click me\n  </div>"
      },
      {
        "ruleId": "vue/sfc-element-order",
